item.description: This One Simple Trick Will Help You Disable Integrated Call Log in iPhone 13 Pro Max! If you’re looking for a way to disable integrated call log in your iPhone 13 Pro Max, you’re in luck! This simple trick will help you easily disable integrated call log in your device, allowing you to keep your call log private and secure. Introduction Overview of Integrated Call Log Integrated call log is a feature in the iPhone 13 Pro Max that stores all of your incoming and outgoing calls in the phone’s memory.
